            <div type="edition">
                <note><p>The assignment of the litanies to the days of the week varies accross manuscripts. The following order reflects that of the modern
                    printed editions. Reference to the days of the week in the manuscript records to these IDs should only be made when the text is available and
                    can be checked. Otherwise, only reference to <ref type="work" corresp="LIT4860Litanies"/> should be made and 
                    the days of the week should be stated in the manuscript record without reference to these sub-IDs.</p>
                    <p>The following text is taken from <bibl><ptr target="bm:1957Qeddase"
                            /><citedRange unit="page">184-188</citedRange></bibl>.</p></note>
                
